01:01:25.557 --> 01:01:26.807
Phillipe Cazal?

01:01:26.892 --> 01:01:28.434
Non.

01:01:31.063 --> 01:01:32.480
Michel Desbordes?

01:01:32.647 --> 01:01:35.232
Listen, gramps, you don't know me.

01:01:35.317 --> 01:01:36.400
Leave me alone, OK?

01:01:44.451 --> 01:01:46.577
