01:04:16.061 --> 01:04:17.728
That's a bad thing?

01:04:17.812 --> 01:04:19.855
He makes the wine
but never drinks it.

01:04:19.940 --> 01:04:21.440
You always drink it.

01:04:21.525 --> 01:04:25.569
Now, why isn't
part of this yours?

01:04:28.240 --> 01:04:30.241
