01:08:15.341 --> 01:08:17.176
I did a long time
ago in school.

01:08:17.260 --> 01:08:19.386
What is it?

01:08:19.470 --> 01:08:22.805
All right, I will
tell you, but...

01:08:22.890 --> 01:08:26.185
First you must take some wine.

01:08:30.273 --> 01:08:31.939
