a hint of sophistication

01:08:43.703 --> 01:08:46.246
and lacking in pretension.

01:08:48.207 --> 01:08:50.876
Actually, I was just
talking about myself.

01:08:52.420 --> 01:08:53.504
I... I don't know.

01:08:53.587 --> 01:08:55.087
No, no, you are not wrong.

01:08:55.173 --> 01:08:57.633
Wine is like people.

01:08:57.716 --> 01:08:59.635
The vine takes
all the influences

01:08:59.719 --> 01:09:01.220
in life all around it.

01:09:01.304 --> 01:09:02.513
It absorbs them,

01:09:02.596 --> 01:09:05.640
and it gets its personality.

01:09:05.725 --> 01:09:06.725
Here.

01:09:09.562 --> 01:09:11.647
Smell.

01:09:11.731 --> 01:09:12.773
Rosemary.

01:09:19.238 --> 01:09:20.279
Some kind of mushroom?

01:09:21.658 --> 01:09:23.325
Very good.

01:09:23.910 --> 01:09:26.245
Currant, cassis, mint,

01:09:27.747 --> 01:09:29.331
lavender,

01:09:29.415 --> 01:09:30.666
they're all in the ground here

01:09:30.750 --> 01:09:31.917
and in the air.

01:09:32.001 --> 01:09:34.586
Now, taste the wine again.

01:09:39.300 --> 01:09:40.509
Close your eyes.

01:09:46.765 --> 01:09:49.350
The currant...

01:09:49.435 --> 01:09:52.062
I can taste that
right away, and...

01:09:52.145 --> 01:09:54.940
