01:10:46.659 --> 01:10:49.953
Whose house is that?

01:10:51.706 --> 01:10:53.707
It's abandoned.

01:10:53.791 --> 01:10:55.083
No one comes here anymore.

01:10:55.168 --> 01:10:56.249
The guy who had this place,

01:10:56.252 --> 01:10:58.712
