when she means "no"

01:14:00.812 --> 01:14:02.896
And vice versa.
Do you understand?

01:14:02.980 --> 01:14:03.980
No.

01:14:04.065 --> 01:14:05.190
You don't?

01:14:06.025 --> 01:14:07.234
Gotcha.

01:14:07.819 --> 01:14:09.694
Now, most important,

01:14:09.779 --> 01:14:11.321
