01:14:11.405 --> 01:14:14.991
he will be expecting
a big scene, a drama.

01:14:15.076 --> 01:14:17.661
You will not give him
the satisfaction.

01:14:17.745 --> 01:14:20.122
This will make him
immediately intrigued.

01:14:20.206 --> 01:14:21.289
