01:16:11.734 --> 01:16:13.193
Well, he's a doctor...

01:16:13.277 --> 01:16:14.236
Like me.

01:16:14.320 --> 01:16:16.571
Except he's a psychiatrist.

01:16:26.165 --> 01:16:27.874
I'll be right back.

01:16:27.959 --> 01:16:29.459
Please, Charlie, sit down.

01:16:53.901 --> 01:16:54.943
