a chance with Charlie

01:20:34.246 --> 01:20:35.997
after what happened earlier?

01:20:38.083 --> 01:20:39.584
Yes, of course.

01:20:40.753 --> 01:20:42.128
And tomorrow...

01:20:42.213 --> 01:20:45.256
